data.title: Milledgeville GA funeral home and cremation
data.meta_description: Obituaries - Slater's Funeral Home offers a variety of funeral services, from traditional funerals to competitively priced cremations, serving Milledgeville, GA and the surrounding communities. We also offer funeral pre-planning and carry a wide selection of caskets, vaults, urns and burial containers.
